'''莫妮卡·萨米勒·莱温斯基'''（{{lang-en|Monica Samille Lewinsky}}，{{bd|1973年|7月23日}}）是一名美国活动家，电视人物，时装设计师和前白宫实习生。在1995年和1996年于[[白宫|白宫]]工作时，[[美国总统|美国总统]][[比尔·克林顿|比尔·克林顿]]承认与她存在所谓的“不正当关系”。这一事件及其后果，包括[[克林顿弹劾案|克林顿弹劾案]]，成为著名的[[陸文斯基醜聞|陸文斯基醜聞]]。

由于丑闻的影响，莱温斯基成为国际知名人物。她随后从事各种事业，包括以她的名字设计一系列手提包，成为饮食计划的广告代言人，担任电视人物，然后远离公众焦点，于伦敦攻读心理学硕士。她也因丑闻在网上被人公开嘲笑。2014年，她以社会活动家的身份重回公众视野，讨论丑闻的影响以及反对[[网络欺凌|网络欺凌]]。

==早年经历==
莫妮卡·萨米勒·莱温斯基出生于美国[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[旧金山|旧金山]]，在洛杉矶西部[[布伦特伍德|布伦特伍德]]和[[贝弗利山|比弗利山]]的一个富裕家庭长大<ref name="Morton1999">{{cite book |last=Morton |first=Andrew R. |authorlink=Andrew Morton (writer) |title=Monica's Story |url=https://archive.org/details/monicasstory00mort |year=1999 |publisher=St. Martin's Press |location=New York |isbn=0-312-97362-4 |page=357}}</ref><ref name="WashpoProfile">{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/politics/special/clinton/stories/lewprofile.htm|title=Lewinsky: Two Coasts, Two Lives, Many Images|author=Leen, Jeff|date=1998-01-24|newspaper=[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]]|page=A1|accessdate=2013-08-17|archive-date=2008-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080907170242/http://washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/politics/special/clinton/stories/lewprofile.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="cnn-whois">{{cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/ALLPOLITICS/1998/08/06/lewinsky.profile/ |title=Who Is Monica Lewinsky? |author=Aiken, Jonathan |publisher=CNN |date=1998-08-06 |accessdate=2013-08-17 |archive-date=2018-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181030011805/http://www.cnn.com/ALLPOLITICS/1998/08/06/lewinsky.profile/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="jta">{{cite news|url=http://www.jweekly.com/article/full/7521/l-a-temple-fends-off-lewinsky-inquiries/|title=L.A. temple fends off Lewinsky inquiries|author=Tugend, Tom|date=1998-01-30|newspaper=[[j.|j.]]|agency=[[Jewish_Telegraphic_Agency|Jewish Telegraphic Agency]]|accessdate=2013-08-17|archive-date=2010-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100221094718/http://www.jweekly.com/article/full/7521/l-a-temple-fends-off-lewinsky-inquiries/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。她的父亲[[伯纳德·莱温斯基|伯纳德·莱温斯基]]（Bernard Lewinsky）是一名[[肿瘤学|肿瘤学家]]，祖父是[[德国犹太人|德国犹太人]]，在14岁时逃离纳粹党执政下的[[德国|德国]]，搬到中美洲国家[[萨尔瓦多|萨尔瓦多]]，然后到达北美<ref name="WashpoProfile" /><ref name="mworld">{{cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/ALLPOLITICS/1998/02/23/time/pooley.html |title=Monica's World |author=Pooley, Eric |magazine=Time |date=1998-02-23}}</ref>。母亲本名玛西娅·卡伊·维伦斯基（Marcia Kay Vilensky），是一名作家，笔名玛西娅·刘易斯（Marcia Lewis）。1996年，她出版了唯一的著作，[[八卦新闻|八卦]]传记《三位贵族的私人生活》（''The Private Lives of the Three Tenors''）。刘易斯曾“暗示”（未证实）她曾与歌剧明星[[普拉西多·多明哥|普拉西多·多明戈]]有染。在莱温斯基丑闻期间，新闻界拿此事与她女儿和克林顿的性关系作比较。<ref name="WaPo">{{cite news|last1=Leen|first1=Jeff|title=Role Puts Spotlight on Lewinsky's Mother|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/politics/special/clinton/stories/lewis020498.htm|accessdate=2015-08-02|publisher=Washington Post|date=1998-02-04}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Cooper|first1=Richard T.|last2=La Ganga|first2=Maria|last3=Nelson|first3=Jack|title=Monica's Mom, the Reluctant Starr Witness|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1998/apr/02/news/ls-35076/2|accessdate=2015-08-02|publisher=Los Angeles Times|date=1998-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151123214805/http://articles.latimes.com/1998/apr/02/news/ls-35076/2|archive-date=2015-11-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="Kelly">{{cite news|last=Kelly|first=Keith J.|title=Mom's Tenor Tale Teased Us|accessdate=2015-08-02|newspaper=[[New_York_Daily_News|New York Daily News]]|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/news/mom-tenor-tale-teased-article-1.793165|date=1998-01-24|archive-date=2015-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151124150251/http://www.nydailynews.com/archives/news/mom-tenor-tale-teased-article-1.793165|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Kamiya">{{cite web|last=Kamiya|first=Gary|title=Mommy Leerest|publisher=[[Salon.com|Salon]]|date=1998-01-23}}</ref>莫妮卡的外祖父塞缪尔·M·维伦斯基（Samuel M. Vilensky）是[[立陶宛犹太人|立陶宛犹太人]]，外祖母布罗尼亚·波尔肖克 （Bronia Poleshuk）出生于中国[[天津|天津]]英租界的一个俄罗斯犹太家庭<ref>{{cite news |url=http://articles.nydailynews.com/1998-08-09/news/18078775_1_monica-lewinsky-friends-marcia-lewis |title=Monica's Mom Defended |date=1998-08-09 |newspaper=[[紐約每日新聞|Daily News]] |location=New York |accessdate=2017-07-09 |archive-date=2012-07-07 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120707135201/http://articles.nydailynews.com/1998-08-09/news/18078775_1_monica-lewinsky-friends-marcia-lewis |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="nypost">{{cite news |author=Italiano, Laura |title=Monica's mother's breakdown revealed |url=http://www.nypost.com/p/news/monica_mother_breakdown_revealed_QaoQxqfTHKvzk6omyM2NoL |newspaper=[[紐約郵報|New York Post]] |date=1998-10-03 |accessdate=2017-07-09 |archive-date=2011-05-10 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20110510075915/http://www.nypost.com/p/news/monica_mother_breakdown_revealed_QaoQxqfTHKvzk6omyM2NoL |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://articles.latimes.com/1998/apr/02/news/ls-35076/2 |work=Los Angeles Times |title=Monica's Mom, the Reluctant Starr Witness |date=1998-04-02 |access-date=2017-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151123214805/http://articles.latimes.com/1998/apr/02/news/ls-35076/2 |archive-date=2015-11-23 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。莫妮卡父母于1987年至1988年期间的分居与离婚对她造成了很大的影响<ref name="WashpoProfile" /><ref name="people">{{cite news|url=http://www.people.com/people/archive/article/0,,20124429,00.html|title=Scandal at 1600|author=Green, Michelle|date=1998-02-09|magazine=[[人物_(雜誌)|People]]}}</ref>。她的父亲后来娶了现在的妻子芭芭拉（Barbara）<ref name="jta" />。母亲后来与总统[[吉米·卡特|吉米·卡特]]掌管的[[美国之音|美国之音]]的媒体执行官和前导演R·彼得·斯特劳斯（R. Peter Straus）结婚<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/ALLPOLITICS/1998/02/02/monica.mom/|title=Lewinsky's mother to wed media executive|date=1998-02-02|publisher=CNN}}</ref>。

家人去洛杉矶的西奈神庙（Sinai Temple）祭拜，莫妮卡在其宗教学校西奈秋叶学院（Sinai Akiba Academy）读书<ref name="jta" />。她的小学生涯在[[贝莱尔_(洛杉矶)|贝莱尔]]（ Bel-Air）的约翰·托马斯·戴伊学校度过<ref name="Wire">At Pacific Hills School (formerly Bel-Air Prep) she won the "Outstanding Junior of the Year" award. [http://weeklywire.com/ww/03-15-99/memphis_book.html "That Girl"] by Leonard Gill, March 15, 1999. ''Memphis Flyer'' book review. Retrieved December 18, 2006.</ref>。后来她进入[[比佛利山庄高中|比佛利山高中]]（Beverly Hills High School）学习，但她最后一年转校至贝莱尔预备学校（Bel Air Prep，后来被称为太平洋山学校（Pacific Hills School））并于1991年毕业<ref name="WashpoProfile" /><ref name="cnn-whois" />。

高中毕业后，莱温斯基就读于两年制社区学院[[圣莫尼卡学院|圣莫尼卡学院]]（Santa Monica College），并在比弗利山庄高中戏剧系和一家领带店工作<ref name="WashpoProfile" /><ref name="people" />。1992年，她据称与已婚前高中戏剧导师安迪·布雷勒（Andy Bleiler）开始了为期五年的恋情<ref name="wapo-bleiler">{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/politics/special/clinton/stories/drama012898.htm|title=Lewinsky's Former Teacher Discloses Affair|last=Clairborne|first=William|date=1998-01-28|newspaper=[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]]|page=A22}}</ref>。1993年，她入读[[俄勒冈州|俄勒冈州]][[波特兰|波特兰]]的[[刘易斯克拉克学院|刘易斯克拉克学院]]（Lewis & Clark College），1995年毕业获心理学学士学位<ref name="WashpoProfile" /><ref name="cnn-whois" /><ref name="people" />。

在家里关系的帮助下，莱温斯基获得了在[[白宮幕僚長|白宫幕僚长]][[莱昂·帕内塔|莱昂·帕内塔]]办公室的无薪夏季实习机会。莱温斯基搬到华盛顿特区，于1995年7月就职<ref name="WashpoProfile" /><ref name="people" />。1995年12月，她获得了[[白宫办公厅|白宫法律事务办公室]]的有薪职位<ref name="WashpoProfile" />。

==丑闻==
{{Main|萊文斯基醜聞}}
[[File:Bill_Clinton_and_Monica_Lewinsky_on_February_28,_1997_A3e06420664168d9466c84c3e31ccc2f.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:Monica_lewinsky.jpg|thumb]]
莱温斯基称，1995年11月至1997年3月期间，她与时任总统[[比尔·克林顿|比尔·克林顿]]发生了九次性接触。根据她的证词，在[[椭圆形办公室|椭圆形办公室]]发生[[咂陽|口交]]和其他性行为，但没有[[性交|性交]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/news/politics/2008-03-19-852575883_x.htm|title=Lewinsky and the first lady|date=2008-03-19|work=USA Today|accessdate=2010-01-19|agency=Associated Press|archive-date=2010-04-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100412161707/http://www.usatoday.com/news/politics/2008-03-19-852575883_x.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

克林顿曾在任[[阿肯色州|阿肯色州]]州长期间遭到性行为不端的指控，其中包括前阿肯色州雇员{{le|保拉·琼斯|Paula Jones}}对他提起民事诉讼，声称他曾经对她进行性骚扰。在琼斯案的审理阶段，莱温斯基的名字浮出水面，当时琼斯的律师试图表明克林顿的行为模式，包括与其他政府雇员发生性关系。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=Xq9fAAAAIBAJ&sjid=mOYFAAAAIBAJ&pg=3866,13572|title=Paula Jones' lawyers want Lewinsky evidence|date=1998-04-01|newspaper=[[Gettysburg_Times|Gettysburg Times]]|agency=[[美联社|Associated Press]]|page=A3}}</ref>

1996年4月，莱温斯基的上级觉得她在克林顿身上花了太多时间，于是将她从白宫调到[[五角大楼|五角大楼]]<ref name="WashpoProfile" />。她在五角大楼发言人{{le|肯尼思·培根|Kenneth Bacon}}的助理<ref name="WashpoProfile" />。莱温斯基把她与总统的关系告诉了同事{{le|琳达·崔普|Linda Tripp}}。1997年9月起，崔普开始秘密记录关于莱温斯基和克林顿秘密关系的电话对话。1997年12月，莱温斯基从五角大楼离职。<ref name="cnn-know">{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/ALLPOLITICS/1998/01/31/credibility/index.html|title=Keeping Score In the Lewinsky Matter|date=1998-01-31|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]}}</ref>1998年1月，莱温斯基在保拉·琼斯案中提交了书面证词，否认与克林顿存在任何肉体关系，并试图说服崔普撒谎。崔普向独立律师{{le|肯尼思·斯塔尔|Kenneth Starr}}提供了录音带，补充了他对[[白水事件|白水争议]]正在进行的调查。之后斯塔尔扩大了他的调查范围，涉及到莱温斯基、克林顿等人在琼斯案中可能的[[偽證罪|伪证罪]]和唆使他人作伪证罪。崔普把录音对话交给了文学经纪人{{Le|卢西安·戈尔德贝格|Lucianne Goldberg}}。她还说服莱温斯基存下克林顿送给她的礼物，不要干洗，后来这件礼物被称为“蓝色连衣裙”。克林顿宣誓后否认与莱温斯基有过“性关系”。<ref name="starr">[http://icreport.access.gpo.gov/report/6narrit.htm#L1 Starr Report: ''Nature of President Clinton's Relationship with Monica Lewinsky''] {{Wayback|url=http://icreport.access.gpo.gov/report/6narrit.htm#L1 |date=20001203073600 }} Retrieved December 18, 2006.</ref>

克林顿 - 莱温斯基关系的新闻于1998年1月爆出。1998年1月26日，克林顿在全国直播的白宫新闻发布会上说：“我和那个女人——莱温斯基小姐——没有发生性关系。”<ref name="ls-nh">''[[PBS新聞一小時|The NewsHour with Jim Lehrer]]'': [http://www.pbs.org/newshour/bb/white_house/jan-june98/clinton_1-21.html President Bill Clinton January 21, 1998] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pbs.org/newshour/bb/white_house/jan-june98/clinton_1-21.html |date=20080207152841 }}</ref>此事立即占据了各大新闻媒体头条，而莱温斯基在接下来的几个星期住在她母亲在[[水门综合大厦|水门综合大厦]]的住所，躲避公众的关注<ref name="mworld" />。莱温斯基与布雷勒的关系也被扒出，他向斯塔尔转交了莱温斯基入职白宫期间给他和他妻子的各种纪念品、照片和文件。<ref name="wapo-bleiler" /><ref name="cnn-know" />

克林顿还表示，“不存在性关系、不正当的性关系或任何其他不正当的关系”（there is not a sexual relationship, an improper sexual relationship or any other kind of improper relationship）<ref name="ls-nh" /><ref name="wapo081898">{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/politics/special/clinton/stories/clinton081898.htm|title=Clinton Admits to Lewinsky Relationship, Challenges Starr to End Personal 'Prying'|last=Baker|first=Peter|date=1998-08-18|work=[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]]|author2=John F. Harris|page=A1|accessdate=2013-08-17|archive-date=2006-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061004120050/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/politics/special/clinton/stories/clinton081898.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，他在1998年8月17日辩解道这是事实。因为其使用[[現在式|现在时态]]，有个著名的争论是“这取决于‘is’的含义是什么”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://jurist.law.pitt.edu/transcr.htm|title=Videotaped Testimony of William Jefferson Clinton Before the Grand Jury Empaneled for Independent Counsel Kenneth Starr August 17, 1998|accessdate=2013-01-05|date=1998-09-21|publisher=JURIST: The Law Professors' Network|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110711175656/http://jurist.law.pitt.edu/transcr.htm|archivedate=2011-07-11|last1=Hibbitts|first1=Bernard}}</ref>（即在他发表声明时，他已不再与莱温斯基保持性关系）。斯塔尔从莱温斯基那得到了有克林顿[[精液|精斑]]的蓝色连衣裙，借此对克林顿施压。莱温斯基也作证道总统曾在她的阴道里插过一支雪茄管。最后克林顿说：“我确实和莱温斯基小姐有过不正当的关系。”<ref name="wapo081898" />克林顿否认犯有伪证罪，根据克林顿的说法，口交的法律定义<ref name="sex-definition">[http://www.huppi.com/kangaroo/L-clintonjonesperjury.html "Perjury about sexual relations from the Paula Jones deposition"] by Steve Kangas. Retrieved February 12, 2006</ref>本身并不包括在“性”之中。此外，依据由检方提出、经辩方同意并由苏珊·韦伯·赖特（Susan Webber Wright）法官公示的“性关系”定义，克林顿声称由于某些行为是对他进行而非由他实行，所以没有涉及性关系。然而，莱温斯基对斯塔尔委员会的证词与克林顿在性接触中被完全被动的说法相矛盾。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1998/09/20/us/testing-president-overview-lawyers-say-tape-clinton-shows-regret-anger.html?pagewanted=all|title=The Testing of a President: The Overview; Lawyers Say Tape of Clinton Shows Regret and Anger|last=Bennet|first=James|date=1998-09-20|last2=Abramson|first2=Jill|newspaper=The New York Times|accessdate=2017-07-09|archive-date=2016-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306191013/http://www.nytimes.com/1998/09/20/us/testing-president-overview-lawyers-say-tape-clinton-shows-regret-anger.html?pagewanted=all|dead-url=no}}</ref>

克林顿和莱温斯基在[[陪審團|陪审团]]前出庭。克林顿通过闭路电视作证，莱温斯基则亲自前来。[[美国独立律师办公室|美国独立律师办公室]]授予她罪行豁免权，以换取她的证词<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/ALLPOLITICS/1998/07/28/lewinsky/|title=Lewinsky Strikes Far-Reaching Immunity Deal|last=Blitzer|first=Wolf|date=1998-07-28|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|author2=Franken, Bob|accessdate=2013-03-09|archive-date=2011-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110121145022/http://www.cnn.com/ALLPOLITICS/1998/07/28/lewinsky/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==丑闻后的生活==

这件事使莱温斯基卷入政治风暴的中心，成为[[流行文化|流行文化]]名人<ref name="time-where">{{cite news|url=http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,1870544_1870543_1870550,00.html|title=Where Are They Now: The Clinton Impeachment: Monica Lewinsky|date=2009-01-09|accessdate=2010-05-13|magazine=Time|archive-date=2010-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100617060523/http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0%2C28804%2C1870544_1870543_1870550%2C00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她的豁免协议限制了她可以公开谈论的内容，但她能够与[[安德魯·莫頓|安德鲁·莫顿]]（Andrew Morton）合作，让他撰写《莫妮卡的故事》（''Monica's Story''），她的传记包括与克林顿有染的一面<ref name="cnn030899">{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/ALLPOLITICS/time/1999/03/08/makeover.html|title=Monica's makeover|author=Cloud, John|date=1999-03-08|publisher=CNN|accessdate=2017-07-09|archive-date=2011-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110831082058/http://www.cnn.com/ALLPOLITICS/time/1999/03/08/makeover.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="nyt030599">{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/books/99/02/28/daily/030599lewinsky-book-review.html|title='Monica's Story': Tawdry and Tiresome|author=Kakutani, Michiko|date=1999-03-05|authorlink=Michiko Kakutani|newspaper=[[纽约时报|The New York Times]]|accessdate=2017-07-09|archive-date=2017-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170109113643/http://www.nytimes.com/books/99/02/28/daily/030599lewinsky-book-review.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。该书于1999年3月出版，并被《[[時代_(雜誌)|时代]]》杂志选为封面故事<ref name="cnn030899" /><ref name="nyt030599" />。1999年3月3日，[[芭芭拉·沃尔特斯|芭芭拉·沃尔特斯]]于ABC《[[20/20_(节目)|20/20]]》节目采访了莱温斯基。节目吸引7000万美国人观看，破了新闻节目的观看纪录<ref name="cnn030899" />。莱温斯基从书中获利大约50万美元，另外还有100万美元来自接受沃尔特斯（Walters）采访的国际权利，但她仍为高额的法律与生活费用所困扰<ref name="nymag-profile">{{cite news|url=http://nymag.com/nymetro/news/people/features/4481/|title=Monica Takes Manhattan|author=Grigoriadis, Vanessa|date=2001-03-19|magazine=[[New_York_(magazine)|New York]]|accessdate=2017-07-09|archive-date=2014-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140706183225/http://nymag.com/nymetro/news/people/features/4481/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1999年6月，《[[女士_(杂志)|女士]]》杂志刊登了作家苏珊·简·吉尔曼（Susan Jane Gilman）<ref name="Ms1">{{cite news|url=http://www.msmagazine.com/jun99/monica-gilman.asp|title=Oral Report|last=Gilman|first=Susan Jane|date=June 1999|work=[[Ms._Magazine|Ms. Magazine]]|accessdate=2014-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140210003700/http://www.msmagazine.com/jun99/monica-gilman.asp|archive-date=2014-02-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，性学家[[苏西·布莱特|苏西·布莱特]]（Susie Bright）<ref name="Ms2">{{cite news|url=http://www.msmagazine.com/jun99/monica-bright.asp|title=The Beauty and the Brains|last=Bright|first=Susie|date=June 1999|work=[[Ms._Magazine|Ms. Magazine]]|accessdate=2014-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715141323/http://www.msmagazine.com/jun99/monica-bright.asp|archive-date=2014-07-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>和主持人阿比奥拉·阿布拉姆斯（Abiola Abrams）<ref name="Ms3">{{cite news|url=http://www.msmagazine.com/jun99/monica-abrams.asp|title=Dear Monica|last=Adams|first=Abiola Wendy|date=June 1999|work=[[Ms._Magazine|Ms. Magazine]]|accessdate=2014-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140806031850/http://www.msmagazine.com/jun99/monica-abrams.asp|archive-date=2014-08-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>的一系列文章，从三代女性的角度论述了莱温斯基的行为对[[女权主义|女权主义]]的意义。同年，莱温斯基在机场拒绝了签名请求，说“我因为一些不太好的事情出名”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://articles.orlandosentinel.com/1999-02-07/news/9902050766_1_jessica-hahn-fame-monica-lewinsky|title=Monica Gains Respect For Renouncing Fame|author=Leonard Pitts|date=1999-02-07|newspaper=[[Orlando_Sentinel|Orlando Sentinel]]|accessdate=2017-07-09|archive-date=2012-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120701020518/http://articles.orlandosentinel.com/1999-02-07/news/9902050766_1_jessica-hahn-fame-monica-lewinsky|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1999年5月8日，她在NBC的《周六夜现场》的两个小品中客串她自己，节目在过去16个月内一直嘲讽她与克林顿的关系。

根据莱温斯基自己的说法，丑闻期间她通过[[編織|编织]]这一方式在媒体的强烈关注下撑了过来<ref name="nymag-profile" />。1999年9月，她扩大这一兴趣，开始出售一系列带有她名字的手提包<ref name="vogue">{{cite news|url=http://www.vogue.co.uk/news/daily/2004-05/040527-is-the-lewinsky-affair-over-.aspx|title=Is the Lewinsky Affair Over?|date=2004-05-27|magazine=[[时尚_(杂志)|Vogue]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110515071129/http://www.vogue.co.uk/news/daily/2004-05/040527-is-the-lewinsky-affair-over-.aspx|archivedate=2011-05-15}}</ref>，以The Real Monica, Inc（真实的莫妮卡公司）的名义<ref name="nymag-profile" />。他们在网上以及纽约的Henri Bendel、加利福尼亚的Fred Segal和伦敦的The Cross销售<ref name="nymag-profile" /><ref name="vogue" /><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,616490,00.html|title=Monica: It's In the Bag|date=1999-01-12|magazine=[[人物_(雜誌)|People]]|accessdate=2017-07-09|archive-date=2010-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100606231829/http://www.people.com/people/article/0%2C%2C616490%2C00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。莱温斯基经常去路易斯安那州监督制造<ref name="nymag-profile" />。

2000年初，莱温斯基出现在饮食公司Jenny Craig的电视广告中<ref name="nyt122899">{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1999/12/28/business/media-business-advertising-monica-lewinsky-meets-jenny-craig-spokeswoman-born.html|title=Monica Lewinsky Meets Jenny Craig, and a Spokeswoman Is Born|author=Hays, Constance L.|date=1999-12-28|newspaper=[[纽约时报|The New York Times]]|accessdate=2017-07-09|archive-date=2016-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308114855/http://www.nytimes.com/1999/12/28/business/media-business-advertising-monica-lewinsky-meets-jenny-craig-spokeswoman-born.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。这个价值100万美元的代言在当时获得了相当大的宣传<ref name="nymag-profile" />。莱温斯基表示，尽管她渴望恢复私人生活，但她需要用这笔钱偿还法律费用<ref name="bbc041300">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/711920.stm|title=Lewinsky trimmed from slimming ads|date=2000-04-13|publisher=BBC News|accessdate=2017-07-09|archive-date=2010-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100122015835/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/711920.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Jenny Craig的发言人这样描述莱温斯基：“她代表着当今有着繁忙的生活方式、充满活力的女人。而且她有体重问题，长期以来一直与体重做斗争。这代表了美国很多女性的现状。”<ref name="nyt122899" />莱温斯基当代言人后引发了争议，一些产品换成了较旧的广告<ref name="nymag-profile" /><ref name="bbc041300" />。公司于2000年2月停止投放莱温斯基的广告，并于2000年4月完全终止了她的宣传，仅向她支付了30万美元的报酬<ref name="bbc041300" /><ref name="nymag-profile" />。

另外在2000年初，莱温斯基搬到纽约市，住在[[西村_(纽约市)|西村]]，成为[[曼哈頓|曼哈顿]]社交场合的A级客人<ref name="nymag-profile" />。2000年2月，她出现在[[音樂電視網|MTV]]的《汤姆绿色秀》（''The Tom Green Show''）中，主持人将她带到父母[[渥太华|渥太华]]家中，为她的新手提包业务寻找面料。 2000年末，莱温斯基在[[英國第五台|英國第五台]]任记者，在《莫妮卡的明信片》（''Monica's Postcards''）节目上报道美国各地的文化和趋势。<ref name="nymag-profile" /><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.iol.co.za/news/world/now-monica-shows-off-her-postcards-on-uk-tv-1.48592 |title=Now Monica shows off her 'Postcards' on UK TV |agency=[[美联社|Associated Press]]/[[South_African_Press_Association|South African Press Association]] |publisher=[[Independent_Online_(South_Africa)|Independent Online]] |date=2000-09-24 |accessdate=2017-07-09 |archive-date=2011-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110917021754/http://www.iol.co.za/news/world/now-monica-shows-off-her-postcards-on-uk-tv-1.48592 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2002年3月，莱温斯基不再受豁免协议的约束，参加在[[HBO|HBO]]特辑“莫妮卡的黑与白”（Monica in Black and White）<ref name="nymag-profile" />，此为《美国卧底》（''America Undercover''）系列的一部分<ref name="nyt030302">{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2002/03/03/arts/television-radio-telling-her-own-story-selling-her-new-self.html|title=Telling Her Own Story, Selling Her New Self|author=James, Caryn|date=2002-03-03|newspaper=[[纽约时报|The New York Times]]|accessdate=2017-07-09|archive-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160816230849/http://www.nytimes.com/2002/03/03/arts/television-radio-telling-her-own-story-selling-her-new-self.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她回答了现场观众关于她的生活和克林顿的问题<ref name="nyt030302" />。

莱温斯基于2003年主持了[[福克斯电视网|福克斯电视网]]的约会节目《个性先生》（''Mr. Personality''），在节目中向年轻参赛女子提出建议<ref name="time-where" /><ref name="nyt032303">{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2003/04/23/business/media-business-advertising-mr-personality-featuring-monica-lewinsky-draws-young.html|title='Mr. Personality,' featuring Monica Lewinsky, draws the young audience of advertisers' dreams|author=Carter, Bill|date=2003-04-23|authorlink=Bill Carter|newspaper=[[纽约时报|The New York Times]]|accessdate=2017-07-09|archive-date=2016-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307194210/http://www.nytimes.com/2003/04/23/business/media-business-advertising-mr-personality-featuring-monica-lewinsky-draws-young.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一些美国人试图在节目上组织抵制广告商，以抗议莱温斯基利用她的恶名挣钱<ref>{{cite news|title=People|date=2003-04-27|newspaper=[[Saint_Paul_Pioneer_Press|Saint Paul Pioneer Press]]|page=C8}}</ref>。尽管如此，节目首次播出后获得了很高的收视率<ref name="nyt032303" />，亚历山德拉·斯坦利（Alessandra Stanley）在《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》上写道：“经过多年的努力，通过设计手提袋和其他自我营销计划来利用名声赚钱，莱温斯基女士终于在电视上找到了一个合适自己的位置。”<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2003/04/23/arts/the-tv-watch-the-name-of-the-game-is-class-guys-and-gals-or-the-lack-of-it.html|title=The Name of the Game Is Class, Guys and Gals, or the Lack of It|author=Stanley, Alessandra|date=2003-04-23|authorlink=Alessandra Stanley|newspaper=[[纽约时报|The New York Times]]|accessdate=2017-07-09|archive-date=2015-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151123201635/http://www.nytimes.com/2003/04/23/arts/the-tv-watch-the-name-of-the-game-is-class-guys-and-gals-or-the-lack-of-it.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而评分连续多周下滑<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0356281/news|title="Mr. Personality" (2003)|accessdate=2009-10-16|publisher=[[互联网电影数据库|IMDB.com]]|archive-date=2016-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408035722/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0356281/news|dead-url=no}}</ref>，节目完成初期有限运作后，未再重新播出<ref name="imdb">{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0506861/|title=Monica Lewinsky|accessdate=2009-10-16|publisher=[[互联网电影数据库|IMDB.com]]|archive-date=2009-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090122223941/http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0506861/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年，她出现在英国的《V Graham Norton》、瑞典的《High Chaparall》以及美国的《The View》和《[[吉米·坎摩尔直播秀|吉米·坎摩尔直播秀]]》节目中<ref name="imdb" />。

在克林顿的自传《[[我的生活_(比尔·克林顿)|我的生活]]》于2004年出版后，莱温斯基在接受英国小报《[[每日郵報|每日邮报]]》采访时说道<ref name="USAT0625">{{cite news|url=http://www.usatoday.com/life/books/news/2004-06-25-lewinsky-clinton_x.htm|title=Lewinsky: Clinton lies about relationship in his new book|date=2006-06-25|newspaper=[[今日美國|USA Today]]|accessdate=2006-12-18|agency=[[美联社|Associated Press]]|archive-date=2007-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070501061943/http://www.usatoday.com/life/books/news/2004-06-25-lewinsky-clinton_x.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>：
{{Quote|text=他本可以在这本书中纠正错误，但他没有。他是一个历史修正主义者。他撒了谎。[……]我真没指望他会详细介绍我们的关系。[……]但是，如果他这样做了并坦诚说明，我不会介意。[……]不过我至少希望他能够纠正他在保护其总统职位时所做的虚假陈述。相反，他谈到这一点时，好像我把它全部放在那里等他拿。我是自助餐，他只是不能抗拒甜点的诱惑。[……]这是一个相互的关系，各个层面的相互关系，从起点一路走来。[……]对于他必须完全亵渎我的性格的做法，我不能接受。<small>|source=于《每日邮报》采访中的声明</small>|author=莫妮卡·莱温斯基}}

2005年，莱温斯基发现她在美国无法逃离聚光灯，这使她的职业与个人生活变得困难重重<ref name="time-where" />。她停止销售手提包<ref name="vogue" />并搬至伦敦，在[[伦敦经济学院|伦敦政治经济学院]]学习[[社会心理学|社会心理学]]<ref name="time-where" />。2006年12月，莱温斯基毕业，获[[理學碩士|理学硕士]]学位<ref name="LSEgrad">{{cite news|url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,238021,00.html|title=Monica Lewinsky Earns Master's Degree in London|date=2006-12-21|publisher=Fox News|accessdate=2006-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070108173219/http://www.foxnews.com/story/0%2C2933%2C238021%2C00.html|archive-date=2007-01-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/education/2005/sep/07/highereducation.psychology|title=Lewinsky to study psychology at LSE|author=MacLeod, Donald|date=2005-09-07|newspaper=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|accessdate=2009-12-24|location=London|archive-date=2014-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140507020752/http://www.theguardian.com/education/2005/sep/07/highereducation.psychology|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 在接下来的十年里，她竭力避免大众宣传<ref name="time-where" /><ref name="pol-purdum">{{cite news|url=http://www.politico.com/story/2014/05/lewinskys-perspective-106421.html|title=Monica Lewinsky's hard-won perspective|last=Purdum|first=Todd S.|date=2014-05-10|authorlink=Todd Purdum|newspaper=[[Politico|Politico]]|accessdate=2017-07-09|archive-date=2014-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140511000926/http://www.politico.com/story/2014/05/lewinskys-perspective-106421.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.salon.com/2013/07/23/the_monica_lewinsky_scandal_where_are_they_now/|title=The Monica Lewinsky scandal: Where are they now?|author=Gupta, Prachi|date=2013-07-23|accessdate=2013-11-05|magazine=[[Salon_(website)|Salon]]|archive-date=2013-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130923211310/http://www.salon.com/2013/07/23/the_monica_lewinsky_scandal_where_are_they_now/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2009年，莱温斯基在研究克林顿丑闻的学者肯·戈麦利（Ken Gormley）的著作中发声，认为克林顿对关于两人关系的具体问题上说谎<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.politico.com/news/stories/1209/30745.html|title=Monica's back – says Clinton lied|author=Gerstein, Josh|date=2009-12-17|author2=Harris, John F.|newspaper=[[The_Politico|The Politico]]|accessdate=2009-12-24|archive-date=2009-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091220235752/http://www.politico.com/news/stories/1209/30745.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年，布雷勒移交给斯塔尔的与莱温斯基相关的物品被布雷勒的前妻拍卖<ref name="time-items">{{cite news|url=http://newsfeed.time.com/2013/06/25/monica-lewinsky-mementos-go-up-for-auction/|title=Monica Lewinsky Mementos Go Up for Auction|last=Ho|first=Erica|date=2013-06-25|magazine=[[時代_(雜誌)|Time]]|accessdate=2017-07-09|archive-date=2013-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130625221709/http://newsfeed.time.com/2013/06/25/monica-lewinsky-mementos-go-up-for-auction/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在她淡出公众视线的十年间，莱温斯基居住在伦敦、洛杉矶、纽约和波特兰。但是由于她的坏名声，在接受非营利组织通信和营销工作面试时遇到了困难<ref name="pol-purdum" /><ref name="ShameVF">{{cite news|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/style/society/2014/06/monica-lewinsky-humiliation-culture|title=Shame and Survival: Monica Lewinsky on the Culture of Humiliation|last=Lewinsky|first=Monica|date=June 2014|work=Vanity Fair|accessdate=2015-07-01|archive-date=2015-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150704062418/http://www.vanityfair.com/style/society/2014/06/monica-lewinsky-humiliation-culture|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==再现于大众==
[[File:Monica_Lewinsky.jpg|thumb]]演讲，2015年3月]]
2014年5月，莱温斯基在《[[名利场_(杂志)|名利场]]》杂志发表了一篇名为“羞耻与生存”（Shame and Survival）的文章，讨论她的生活和丑闻<ref name="ShameVF" /><ref name="VFpreview">{{cite news|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/online/daily/2014/05/monica-lewinsky-speaks|title=Exclusive: Monica Lewinsky Writes About Her Affair with President Clinton|date=2014-05-06|accessdate=2014-05-07|magazine=[[名利场_(杂志)|Vanity Fair]]|archive-date=2014-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140506233301/http://www.vanityfair.com/online/daily/2014/05/monica-lewinsky-speaks|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她仍然认为这种关系是相互的，写道克林顿利用她，这也是一个自愿的关系<ref name="TheWeekpreview">{{cite web|url=http://theweek.com/article/index/261080/speedreads-monica-lewinsky-breaks-10-years-of-silence-on-affair-with-president-clinton|title=Monica Lewinsky breaks 10 years of silence on affair with President Clinton|accessdate=2014-05-07|date=2014-05-07|last=Meslow|first=Scott|magazine=[[The_Week|The Week]]|archive-date=2014-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140506230937/https://theweek.com/article/index/261080/speedreads-monica-lewinsky-breaks-10-years-of-silence-on-affair-with-president-clinton|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她补充道：“我自己，对我和克林顿总统之间发生的事情深表遗憾。”<ref name="pol-purdum" />杂志后来宣布她成为《名利场》的贡献者，表示她将“持续为他们的网站做贡献，寻找相关感兴趣的主题”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/monica-lewinsky-becomes-vanity-fair-contributor-2014-7|title=Monica Lewinsky Is Writing For Vanity Fair Now|author=Julia Cannon|date=2014-07-31|publisher=businessinsider|accessdate=2015-06-17|archive-date=2015-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617040749/http://www.businessinsider.com/monica-lewinsky-becomes-vanity-fair-contributor-2014-7|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/life-style/monica-lewinsky-contribute-vanity-fair-ongoing-basis-article-1.1888461|title=Monica Lewinsky to contribute to Vanity Fair on an ‘ongoing basis’|author=Beth Stebner|date=2014-08-01|publisher=nydailynews.com|accessdate=2015-06-17|archive-date=2015-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617040706/http://www.nydailynews.com/life-style/monica-lewinsky-contribute-vanity-fair-ongoing-basis-article-1.1888461|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
 
2014年7月，莱温斯基在[[国家地理频道|国家地理频道]]三集电视特辑“90年代：最后的辉煌十年”（''The 90s: The Last Great Decade''）中接受采访。该系列着眼于20世纪90年代的各种事件，包括让莱温斯基成为全国焦点的丑闻。这是莱温斯基十多年来首次接受这样的采访。<ref name="NatGeo">{{cite news|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/online/daily/2014/07/monica-lewinsky-grants-first-tv-interview-in-years|title=Monica Lewinsky Grants First TV Interview in Years|last=Makarechi|first=Kia|date=2014-07-01|accessdate=2014-07-13|magazine=[[名利场_(杂志)|Vanity Fair]]|archive-date=2014-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140712163717/http://www.vanityfair.com/online/daily/2014/07/monica-lewinsky-grants-first-tv-interview-in-years|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2014年10月，她公开反对[[網路霸凌|网络欺凌]]，自称是网上骚扰的“[[指示病例|零号病人]]”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/monica-lewinsky-bullying-victims-dont-suffer-silence/story?id=34139687|title=Monica Lewinsky to Bullying Victims: ‘Please Don’t Suffer in Silence’|date=2015-09-30|publisher=ABC News|accessdate=2017-07-09|archive-date=2016-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160126184414/http://abcnews.go.com/US/monica-lewinsky-bullying-victims-dont-suffer-silence/story?id=34139687|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="cnn1014" />。在《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》杂志“30 Under 30”峰会上，她提及丑闻后的经历，说“撑下来后，我现在想做的就是帮助其他耻辱游戏的受害者坚持下来。”<ref name="cnn1014">{{cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/2014/10/20/politics/lewinsky-cyber-bullying/index.html |title=Lewinsky makes emotional plea to end cyberbullying |last=Merica |first=Dan |date=2014-10-21 |publisher=[[CNN|CNN]] |accessdate=2014-10-22 |archive-date=2014-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022080457/http://www.cnn.com/2014/10/20/politics/lewinsky-cyber-bullying/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="forbes1014">{{cite news|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/clareoconnor/2014/10/20/monica-lewinsky-speaks-its-my-mission-to-end-cyberbullying/|title=Monica Lewinsky Speaks: 'It's My Mission To End Cyberbullying'|last=O'Connor|first=Clare|date=2014-10-20|accessdate=2014-10-22|magazine=[[福布斯|Forbes]]|archive-date=2014-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141021225914/http://www.forbes.com/sites/clareoconnor/2014/10/20/monica-lewinsky-speaks-its-my-mission-to-end-cyberbullying/|dead-url=no}}</ref>她说她看到[[罗格斯大学|罗格斯大学]]新生[[泰勒·克莱蒙泰自杀|泰勒·克莱蒙泰]]（Tyler Clementi）因受网络欺凌而自杀的故事<ref name="cnn1014"/>，受其影响并加入[[Twitter|Twitter]]发声<ref name="forbes1014" /><ref name="cnntwitter">{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2014/10/20/politics/monica-lewinsky-twitter/|title=Monica Lewinsky joins Twitter|last=Merica|first=Dan|date=2014-10-20|publisher=[[CNN|CNN]]|accessdate=2017-07-09|archive-date=2014-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141022101654/http://www.cnn.com/2014/10/20/politics/monica-lewinsky-twitter/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年3月，莱温斯基于[[TED大会|TED]]演讲，继续公开反对网络欺凌<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/03/22/style/monica-lewinsky-is-back-but-this-time-its-on-her-terms.html|title=Monica Lewinsky Is Back, but This Time It’s on Her Terms|last=Bennett|first=Jessica|date=2015-03-19|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2015-03-20|archive-date=2015-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150319224903/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/03/22/style/monica-lewinsky-is-back-but-this-time-its-on-her-terms.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，呼吁建立更加富有同情心的互联网<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-31976567|title=Monica Lewinsky calls for a more compassionate internet|last=Wakefield|first=Jane|date=2015-03-19|work=[[BBC在線|BBC Online]]|accessdate=2015-03-19|archive-date=2015-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150320081006/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/technology-31976567|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H_8y0WLm78U|title=Monica Lewinsky: The price of shame|last=Lewinsky|first=Monica|date=2015-03-20|publisher=[[TED_(conference)|TED]] via [[YouTube|YouTube]]|accessdate=2015-03-21|archive-date=2015-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150321194938/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=H_8y0WLm78U|dead-url=no}}</ref>。6月，她成为反欺凌组织旁观者革命（Bystander Revolution）的大使兼战略顾问<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/monica-lewinsky-joins-antibullying-group-bystander-revolution-says-she-wants-to-help-other-victims-of-the-shame-game-survive-10308313.html|title=Monica Lewinsky joins anti-bullying group Bystander Revolution, says she wants to help 'other victims of the shame game' survive|date=2015-06-09|publisher=The Independent|accessdate=2015-06-17|archive-date=2015-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617062442/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/people/monica-lewinsky-joins-antibullying-group-bystander-revolution-says-she-wants-to-help-other-victims-of-the-shame-game-survive-10308313.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同月，她在[[戛纳国际创意节|戛纳国际创意节]]上发表反网络欺凌演讲<ref>{{cite news|url=http://pagesix.com/2015/06/25/monica-lewinsky-gets-standing-ovation-at-cannes/|title=Monica Lewinsky gets standing ovation at Cannes|date=2015-06-25|publisher=pagesix.com|accessdate=2015-10-02|archive-date=2015-10-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151003183958/http://pagesix.com/2015/06/25/monica-lewinsky-gets-standing-ovation-at-cannes/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。9月，莱温斯基就旁观者革命的“国家欺凌预防月”活动接受《[[早安美國|早安美国]]》[[艾米·罗巴奇|艾米·罗巴奇]]（Amy Robach）的采访<ref>{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/GMA/video/monica-lewinsky-bullying-victims-suffer-silence-34145446|title=Monica Lewinsky Bystander Revolution interview|date=2016-04-29|accessdate=2017-07-09|archive-date=2016-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160705054130/http://abcnews.go.com/GMA/video/monica-lewinsky-bullying-victims-suffer-silence-34145446|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

